full_desc: IF Q1. INRELTO (relationship to participant)=1 (spouse, partner, companion) and Q3. INLIVWTH (lives with participant?)=0 (no)

test_name: INLIVWTH compared to participants living situation
short_desc: IF INLIVWTH=1 then LIVSITUA cannot equal 1
full_desc: IF Q3. INLIVWTH (lives with participant?)=1 (yes) then Form A1, Q12. LIVSITUA (participant's living situation) should not equal 1 (lives alone)

test_name: INMEMWORS aligns with co-participant report on B9
short_desc: If INMEMWORS=1,2 then DECCOGIN should equal 1
full_desc: Q6. INMEMWORS (participant's memory is worse?)=1,2 (Yes) then Form B9, Q4. DECCOGIN (Co-participant-reported cognitive decline) should equal 1 (Yes)

test_name: INMEMTROUB aligns with co-participant report on B9
short_desc: If INMEMTROUB=4,5 then DECCOGIN should equal 1
full_desc: Q7. INMEMTROUB (participant trouble remembering?)=4,5 (Often or very often) then Form B9, Q4. DECCOGIN (Co-participant-reported cognitive decline) should equal 1 (Yes)

test_name: INMEMTEN aligns with co-participant report on B9
short_desc: If INMEMTEN=4,5 then DECCOGIN should equal 1
full_desc: Q8. INMEMTEN (participant's memory compared to 10 years ago?)=4,5 (A little worse or much worse) then Form B9, Q4. DECCOGIN (Co-participant-reported cognitive decline) should equal 1 (Yes)
